    "verification_notes": "Official site gomez.house.gov/contact returned 403. DC phone (202) 225-6235 confirmed across clerk.house.gov, billtrack50, sengov.com, contactgovernors.com, and whoismyrepresentative.com. DC address is 506 Cannon HOB per clerk.house.gov (119th Congress); some older sources show 1530 Longworth (previous congress). District office at 350 S. Bixel St #120, Los Angeles confirmed via VICA directory and BillTrack50. District phone (213) 481-1425 and fax (213) 481-1427 confirmed via VICA and web search results. Note: dc_fax marked needs_review because the (213) 481-1427 fax listed in some sources appears to be the district office fax, not a DC fax; no separate DC fax number found. Twitter @RepJimmyGomez, Facebook RepJimmyGomez, Instagram @repjimmygomez all confirmed via direct social media profiles. Campaign site jimmygomezforcongress.com confirmed. No YouTube channel or Bluesky found."
